Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗介，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說得太過份了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.46,0:21:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了賠罪，要不要一起吃晚飯…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.93,0:21:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你房間裡有女孩子在啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.26,0:21:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一回 FULL METAL PANIC\N「危險的SaFe House」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.83,0:21:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗介，這女孩到底是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.94,0:21:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是潛水艇的艦長大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.34,0:21:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會相信啊！
